741
00:57:53,149 --> 00:57:55,037
Bravo, Don Corleone!

742
00:57:57,520 --> 00:57:58,646
Thank you.

743
00:57:59,856 --> 00:58:03,189
Friends, l have come here...

744
00:58:03,293 --> 00:58:06,956
