754
00:58:45,068 --> 00:58:46,956
you invested and how long for.

755
00:58:47,070 --> 00:58:50,028
Michael,
this is really generous!

756
00:58:50,140 --> 00:58:52,199
Oh, wonderful.

757
00:58:55,311 --> 00:58:59,168
- Hey, Parisi, how much did you invest?
- l don't remember.

758
00:58:59,282 --> 00:59:01,409
Michael, you're blessed.

759
00:59:07,490 --> 00:59:10,789
My family has done
much of the hard work...

760
00:59:10,894 --> 00:59:12,782
taken many risks...

761
00:59:14,430 --> 00:59:17,490
all to make money
for the rest of the families.

762
00:59:19,903 --> 00:59:22,736
